1. spark-submit提交作业

				运行模式            指定yarn队列                   app主类                                    jar包            args
spark-submit --master yarn --queue bonc_songpeiqiang --class scala.spark.job.WordCountLocalApplication scala.common.jar WordCountAppConfig.xml




2. 查看日志
yarn logs -applicationId application_1534471928125_1081


3.spark运行环境设置
-Dspark.master=local[1]
